{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nahdans atfinne Eewu\nfawu Seewu/ un ta tappe\ngrihta/ un dseindeja to\nKäinu/ un fazzija: Es esmu to\nWihrü to KUNGU dabbujuft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta dsinnahs prohjam\nwinna Brahti to Ahbelu dsem-\ndeht / un Ahbels tappe weens\nAwju-Ganns/ bet Käins tappe\nweens Semmes-Kohpajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notifke pehz (zit-\ntahm) Deenahm/ ka Käins no\nteem Semmes Augteem tain\nKUNGAM weenu Uppuri at-\nwedde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbels atwedde arri-\ndsan no fawo Awju pirindsim-\nteem/ unn no winnu Taukeem: Un\ntas KUNGS usluhkoja to Ah-\nbelu un winna Uppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Käinu un winna Up-\npuri wiꞥſch (ſchehligi) ne usluh-\nkoja: Tad eedese Käina Bahr-\nsiba / un winna Waigs nikni\nraudſijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS\nuhs Käinu: Kam tu effi apſcai-\ntees/ un kadeht taws Waigs nik-\nni raugahs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Negg irr tas ta/ ja tu pa-\nreisi darriti / tad buhs Peedoh-\nschanas/bet ja tu ne pareisi dar-\nrifi/ tad gull tee Grehti preeſsch\nDurwin / un winnu Eekahro-\nſhana lauschahs us tew/ bet tu\nwaldt pahr teem. Un Käinsrun-\nnaja ar fawu Brahti Ahbelu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notifke/tad tee Lauka\nbha/ tad zehlehsKäins prettAhbe-\nlm fawu Brahti/ unn nokawe to. dseindeja to Ahnoku / un win-\nusta\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzij\nus Käinu: Kur irr Ahbels taw\nBrahlis? un tas fazzija: Es n\nfinnu/ buhs tad man fawu Brah\nli fargaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: Ko effi t\ndarrijs? Tawa Brahta Affin\nBals us nan brehz no Semmes\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu nolahdehts effi t\nno Semmes/ kas fawn Mut\natplehtufi/ tawa Brahta Affin\nno tawahm Rohkahm taxemt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tu to Semmi stra-\ndafi / tad ta ne wairs tew dol\nfawn Padohmu / Tekkuls u\nBehglis buhti tu wirs Semmes\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Käins fazzija us t\nKUNGU: Manna Noseedsba i\nleelaka / ne ka ta warretu peedol\nta tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi/ tu isdsenni ma\nschodeen no Semmes/ un no ta\nwa Waiga buhs mann pattehp\ntees/ un es buhfchu Tekkuls u\nBehglis wirs Semmes/ un ta\nnotiks/ ka jeb kurſch/ kas man a\nrohd/ manni nokans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzij\nus to: Tadeht/ kursch Käinu n\nkanj / tas taps feptikahrt fo\ndihts: Un tas KUNGS peelik\npee Käinu tahdiu Sihmi / ka u\nkas / winnu atrasdains nokantu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Käins isgahje no t\nKUNGA/ un mitte eekſch tah\nSemmes Nod/ Eedenei pre\nRihteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Käins atfinne faw\nSeewu/ un ta tappe grihta / u\ndseindeja to Ahnoku / un win-\nusta\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
